@startuml
title 受理闭环用例图（功能边界）

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "客户端/前端" as Client
actor "运维/开发者" as Ops

rectangle "Ingest Acceptance Closure" {
  usecase "上传文档并受理\nPOST /api/v1/documents/upload" as UC_Accept
  usecase "查询文档当前状态\nGET /api/v1/documents/{id}/status" as UC_Status
  usecase "查询失败（文档不存在）\n返回 404" as UC_StatusNotFound
}

Client --> UC_Accept
Client --> UC_Status
Ops --> UC_Status

UC_StatusNotFound ..> UC_Status : <<extend>>

note right of UC_Accept
  用例目标：
  1) 校验上传请求
  2) 受理并生成 documentId
  3) 落库初始状态 UPLADED
  4) 返回 ACCEPTED
end note

note right of UC_Status
  用例目标：
  1) 按 documentId 查询状态
  2) 返回当前状态
  3) 未命中时返回 404
end note

@enduml
